name: That's No Moon Tee
description:
"He's headed for that small Moon...."
"That's No Moon... That's a space station."

The timeless line from everyone's favourite Jedi Knight, this T-shirt is a nod to one of the best scenes in one of the greatest Sci-Fi universes of all time.

Obi-Wan knows, and with Tee so do you.


This T-shirt, like all our apparel, is manufactured to the highest quality and hand printed using a manual screen printer. So that means that each Tee is completely unique and produced with our own hands. (aka money, sweat & tears)

The shirt its self is an American Apparel Unisex Fine Jersey Short Sleeve T made from 100% Combed Cotton Jersey 146g / 4.3oz. 

Basically that means it is ultra soft, non-shrinking, premium cotton that feels great to wear and looks even better.

name: Blow Me Tee
description:
There was a time that you had to earn your gaming time with more than just money. 

Cartridges were unreliable and unpredictable, valuable minutes would be spent sharply blowing into them, setting them into the console, switching on and praying to the gaming gods that THIS time it would start. *lines appear across screen*

Sigh. Start again. Repeat until you arrive in pixelated gaming nirvana content in the knowledge that you earnt it.

This tee is a playful wink to retro gaming we grew up with.


This T-shirt, like all our apparel, is manufactured to the highest quality and hand printed using a manual screen printer. So that means that each Tee is completely unique and produced with our own hands. (aka money, sweat & tears)

The shirt its self is an American Apparel Unisex Fine Jersey Short Sleeve T made from 100% Combed Cotton Jersey 146g / 4.3oz. 

Basically that means it is ultra soft, non-shrinking, premium cotton that feels great to wear and looks even better.

name: Pixel Heart Tee
description:
Calling all geekettes!

This Tee lets you express your inner geek and show it off in style!
A call back to the glory days of 8/16bit gaming our Pixelated heart emblem oozes geek-chic-goodness.

Best of all its on a premium quality B&C Ladies specific t-shirt, complete with stylish gathered-capped sleeved, ladies fit and heather effect colouring.


This T-shirt, like all our apparel, is manufactured to the highest quality and hand printed using a manual screen printer. So that means that each Tee is completely unique and produced with our own hands. (aka money, sweat & tears)

The shirt its self is a B&C Too Chic T-Shirt made from 100% ringspun cotton, 150gsm, meaning it is super soft, non-shrinking, premium cotton that feels great to wear and looks even better.

name: KEEP CALM & KILL ZOMBIES Tee
description:
Should you find yourself waking up to a new world populated with the walking (or running) undead, then you'll be extremely glad that you possess this Tee.

For the T-shirt is crucial for your survival. It will remind you of the most important rule, to ensuring you making it through the perilous journey to the next safe house... above all other things you must always.. 

Keep calm, and kill zombies*.

If you dont already own one of these tees then our advice is to buy one as soon as possible, remember.. the Zompocalypse could happen at any moment.


*Sever the head or destroy the brain.


This T-shirt, like all our apparel, is manufactured to the highest quality and hand printed using a manual screen printer. So that means that each Tee is completely unique and produced with our own hands. (aka money, sweat & tears)

Basically that means it is ultra soft, non-shrinking, premium cotton that feels great to wear and looks even better.

name: 8bit Heroes Poster
description:
8bit Heroes (GEEK TEST) A2 Poster 

A true test for a true geek. Can you name all the characters and their origins? Challenge your friends! Find out which of you can be crowned the biggest nerd.

Also.. looks cool and is a great quality print.

A sealed cheat sheet wIll be provided... just incase it bests you!

Printing to the highest standard on premium paper with a professional matte laminate finish. These are stunning examples of printed artwork.

name: DUBface Tee
description:
Congratulations on finding this tee, with it you will have your very own DUBface.

DUBface is like text speak but not really lame.
He likes Sci-Fi films, online gaming, dub step music, cotton & enjoys long walks in the countryside.

He doesn't eat, drink or speak but he is a brilliant listener and, provided you treat him right, will always be there to talk to.

This T-shirt, like all our apparel, is manufactured to the highest quality and hand printed using a manual screen printer. So that means that each Tee is completely unique and produced with our own hands. (aka money, sweat & tears)

name: Companion Cubed Tee
description:
You are either in love with the weighted companion cube.. Or you haven't played Portal. And are dead to us.

If however you are in actual, real-life, love with the Companion cube, like we are, then you need to acquire one of these. A symbol of your unfaltering devotion to the cube you sent tumbling down an incineration shoot faster then any other test subject on record.

GLaDOS doesn't want you to get this tee.. Even more reason to wear one with pride.

This T-shirt, like all our apparel, is manufactured to the highest quality and hand printed using a manual screen printer. So that means that each Tee is completely unique and produced with our own hands. (aka money, sweat & tears)

Basically that means it is super soft, non-shrinking, premium cotton that feels great to wear and looks even better.

name: Know Your Space Craft Poster
description:
Know Your Space Craft (GEEK TEST) A2 Poster 

Any sci-fi geek worth their salt knows what an X-wing looks like… but can you name all these iconic spacecraft? Only the purest of Sci-Fi nerds will succeed.

Inspired by the Battle Of Britain ‘Know your aircraft’ posters This poster will tell you whose friendly and who to avoid, to help keep you alive out in deep space.

Challenge extended....

Printing to the highest standard on premium paper with a professional matte laminate finish. These are stunning examples of printed artwork.

name: WUBx3 Tee
description:
The WUBx3 Tee is a T-shirt dedicated to Claptrap's dubstep song!

These stirring lyrics represent a generation... of skanked out, wub-wubbing fiends. Dubstep is taking over the world.. so you might as well join the winning team!

WUB WUB WUB

name: Undo Tee
description:
Arguably THE single most used, and useful, tool in a designer/editor/typist/computer-user's arsenal... 

The Cmd+Z command a.k.a. The UNDO button.

This Tee is a show of appreciation for the ever useful ability to fix our stupid mistakes and indulge our hair-brained ideas. Here's to the key combination that affords us the luxury of 'seeing what that would look like if..' and being able to effortlessly recover from what would be complete disaster!

Where would we be without you UNDO... 

...probably out of a job.

This T-shirt, like all our apparel, is manufactured to the highest quality and hand printed using a manual screen printer. So that means that each Tee is completely unique and produced with our own hands. (aka money, sweat & tears)

name: Ace Tee
description:
Our favourite quote from everyone's favourite Pet Detective... 

The life motto of a generation.

Wearing this T-shirt is a statement of your independence. You are someone who runs (or walks) at their own pace through life. You will not be shepherded into 'timeframes', 'deadlines' or 'pre-arranged-meeting-times' like the rest. You alone command the power to decide when, and if, you arrive at your chosen destination.

It also looks nice.

name: KEEP CALM Tote Bags
description:
White Keep Calm and Kill Zombies Tote Bags

With Ctrl Alt Defeat's Keep Calm & Kill Zombies tote bag you can finally keep all your zombie apocalypse survival gear together! 

The tote bags long sling design grants easy access to items such as painkillers, cricket bats, bandages and anything else your sure to need if planning on surviving the undead nightmare.

Also the bags are made from 100% cotton and are super friendly for the environment. So you can help save the world in two ways.

name: Pixel Heart Tote Bag
description:
The perfect bag for a Geekette!

Just like the Tee this tote shares its design with, the pixelated heart is not only a message of supreme geeky-ness but also a chic fashion symbol.

Here are just some of the advantages of a Tote bag.. They look awesome, they can rolled up and carried to be used when shopping, they dont kill our planet like plastic bags, they last longer then pastic bags and they dont suck like plastic bags do.

These awesome Tote bags are made from 100% organic cotton and are best buds with the environment.

name: Ctrl Alt Defeat Vinyl Sticker
description:
Want to personalise your belongings with our awesome designs?

We love you, and so will everyone else who sees your personalised gear.

Easy to apply & with super simple instructions included.. we especially like to put them on our snowboards, windows, laptops, and even car bumpers.

These are professionally cut, high quality, vinyl decals that will stick very well and be removed easily, leaving little or no residue! Provided, of course, that they are applied correctly to an appropriate smooth and flat surface.
